description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'How To Start Calisthenics at Home for Beginners (No Equipment)' from the channel Adam Frater.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
